1. *Prestao* je da radi kad je dobio otpust iz firme. (He stopped working when he got fired from the company.)

2. Ona je *prestala* da se igra kad je čula mamu. (She stopped playing when she heard her mom.)

3. Oni su *prekinuli* svoje veze. (They broke off their relationship.)

4. *Prestaje* da se ljuti kad razume situaciju. (She stops getting angry when she understands the situation.)

5. *Prestajući* da plače, on je otišao napolje. (Stopping crying, he went outside.)